/-!
# The char-0 additive energy `E33(μ_n)`: exact closed form (#444, avenue L2)

This extends the verified char-0 closed-form ladder one rung beyond `E_32`. It records the
exact cross-polytope / Lam--Leung polynomial at depth `r = 33`, plus the Wick bound and a
strict positive cushion. The positivity certificate starts at `n = 11`, covering the dyadic
support range `n = 2`, `n = 4`, `n = 8`, or `n ≥ 11`. This is deliberately only a
char-0 rung; it does not assert the char-p transfer that forms the #444 BGK/Paley wall.
-/

namespace ProximityGap.Frontier.E33ClosedForm

